&lt;li&gt;Strong verbal and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work effectively with a cross functional and multidisciplinary team environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel up to 10%.&lt;/li&gt;
